\[|g(\overline{x}_{t})-\tilde{g}_{t}^{\overline{x}}|\leq L_{g}\cdot\left[ \left(\frac{\epsilon}{3L_{g}}\right)^{\nicefrac{{1}}{{\beta}}}\right]^{\beta }=\frac{\epsilon}{3}.\]

